---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Pricing — ZENZKO">
  <Header />

  <div class="container-narrow form-page legal-page">
    <p class="eyebrow">Pricing</p>
    <h1 style="font-size:28px; margin-bottom:20px;">Pricing</h1>

    <p>There's no monthly fee and no cost to create or publish a store. We only make money when you do — fees apply per completed sale.</p>

    <h2>Fees per sale</h2>
    <table class="fee-table">
      <tbody>
        <tr>
          <td>Stripe processing fee</td>
          <td>2.65% + NZ$0.30</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td>ZENZKO fee</td>
          <td>1%</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="fee-total">
          <td>Total</td>
          <td>3.65% + NZ$0.30</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>
    <p class="legal-page-note">The ZENZKO fee is 1% while we're in testing. This rate may change as the product develops — any change will be posted here first.</p>

    <h2>What that looks like</h2>
    <p>On a NZ$20.00 sale: Stripe takes NZ$0.83 (2.65% + NZ$0.30) and ZENZKO takes NZ$0.20 (1%), so NZ$18.97 lands in your Stripe account.</p>

    <h2>Where the money goes</h2>
    <p>Payments go straight to your own Stripe account — we never hold your money. The Stripe fee is Stripe's standard New Zealand processing rate for domestic cards; international cards and currency conversion may cost more, per <a href="https://stripe.com/nz/pricing" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Stripe's pricing</a>.</p>

    <h2>Unlocked stores</h2>
    <p>Published stores are locked by default. A one-time upgrade to unlock editing after publishing is coming soon — sale fees stay the same either way.</p>

    <div class="form-actions" style="margin-top:32px;">
      <a class="btn-primary" href="/create">Create your store</a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .fee-table{
    width: 100%;
    border-collapse: collapse;
    font-size: 14.5px;
    margin: 0 0 14px;
  }
  .fee-table td{
    padding: 10px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--line);
  }
  .fee-table td:last-child{
    text-align: right;
    font-family: 'IBM Plex Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 13.5px;
  }
  .fee-table .fee-total td{
    border-bottom: none;
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
